    "created_at": "2026-02-09T20:47:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-02-09T20:47:33Z",
    "body": "One modification to the [suggested fix by danbugs](https://github.com/starship/starship/issues/5816#issuecomment-2845994291). tmux subshells don't work when `__STARSHIP_ALREADY_INIT ` is exported as an env var, so set it as a local variable instead:\n```\nif [ -z \"$__STARSHIP_ALREADY_INIT\" ]; then\n    eval \"$(starship init bash)\"\n    __STARSHIP_ALREADY_INIT=1\nfi\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
